of God's family.

01:04:43.038 --> 01:04:44.117
So I thank you very much.

01:04:44.177 --> 01:04:45.898
I thank the weather for holding off so

01:04:45.938 --> 01:04:47.298
we were able to get this program on.

01:04:47.358 --> 01:04:49.659
I thank you, dear Cara,

01:04:49.699 --> 01:04:52.900
for not chewing on the cable anymore and

01:04:52.920 --> 01:04:54.240
being a good listener.

01:04:55.442 --> 01:04:56.541
My dog, Asher,

01:04:56.581 --> 01:04:58.742
here at my feet as well,

01:04:59.222 --> 01:05:01.023
although I think Wookie has walked away

01:05:01.063 --> 01:05:05.684
now that I squandered the remaining of his

01:05:05.784 --> 01:05:06.284
chew toy.

01:05:08.094 --> 01:05:08.655
Nonetheless,

01:05:09.054 --> 01:05:10.795
I have enjoyed spending this hour with

01:05:10.815 --> 01:05:10.936
you.

01:05:11.235 --> 01:05:12.797
I hope you've gained something from it.

01:05:12.976 --> 01:05:14.516
I hope that I've been able to share

01:05:15.016 --> 01:05:17.217
what I have come to learn from Yahowah

01:05:17.237 --> 01:05:19.378
in a way that enhances your life,

01:05:19.478 --> 01:05:22.800
enhances your understanding of Yahowah and

01:05:22.940 --> 01:05:26.981
our place in His universe that He has

01:05:27.581 --> 01:05:30.742
given to us so that we,

01:05:30.862 --> 01:05:33.242
from our stance in this material realm,

01:05:33.722 --> 01:05:35.364
can literally launch ourselves

01:05:36.224 --> 01:05:37.771
into the stars and up to heaven.

01:05:38.536 --> 01:05:39.561
Thank you for listening.

01:05:39.601 --> 01:05:39.842
Good day.